SENATE BILL 2269
By Briggs
HOUSE BILL 2105
By Moon
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 5 and
Title 6, relative to county government.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 5-5-105(a)(3), is amended by
deleting "forty-eight (48)" and substituting "seventy-two (72)".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
